profile.longBusinessSummary: Roth CH Acquisition IV Co. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to acquire companies operating in the business services, consumer, healthcare, technology, wellness, and sustainability sectors. Roth CH Acquisition IV Co. was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Newport Beach, California.
